text: ( Source : Paul Ryan ) WASHINGTON, DC - This afternoon, Wisconsin 's First District Congressman and Ways and Means Chairman Paul Ryan appeared on MSNBC 's Meet the Press Daily with Chuck Todd to discuss his support of Kevin McCarthy for Speaker,
